\": 0.9969258449022249, \"rank\": 0.002663249743201641, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bam Adebayo showed the way with 18 points, 7 rebounds, and 2 blocks as the Americans won comfortably this time after beating the South Sudanese by just a single point in anexhibition gamebefore the Olympics.\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.773951847264686e-13, \"text\": \"Adebayo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\"}, {\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demographics_of_South_Sudan\", \"score\": 0.716226688986195, \"rank\": 0.3962059992704461, \"text\": \"South Sudanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demographics_of_South_Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demographics_of_South_Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory secured the defending champions a quarterfinal spot after staying as the only unbeaten team in Group C at 2-0.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_C\", \"score\": 0.9949418741498824, \"rank\": 0.003904284696089289, \"text\": \"Group C\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_C\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_C\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Sudan fell to 1-1 and tied Serbia, which made easy work of winless Puerto Rico, 107-66, in the earlier Group C match.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999736255635, \"rank\": 2.628